graph LR
    CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator<br/>v1.15.0]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    CodeFlare -->|base cluster mgmt| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.2.1<br/>REQUIRED]
    CodeFlare -->|TLS cert rotation| CertController[cert-controller<br/>v0.12.0<br/>REQUIRED]
    CodeFlare -->|API calls| K8s[Kubernetes<br/>1.31+<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies - Optional
    CodeFlare -.->|batch scheduling| Kueue[Kueue<br/>v0.10.1+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    CodeFlare -.->|OAuth + Routes| OpenShift[OpenShift<br/>4.11+<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|config reads| ODHOp[ODH Operator<br/>DSCInitialization]
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI triggers| CodeFlare

    %% Integration Points
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes metrics| CodeFlare
    CodeFlare -->|creates CRs| KubeRay
    CodeFlare -->|updates status| Kueue

    %% Managed Resources
    CodeFlare -->|manages| RayClusters[RayCluster CRs<br/>ray.io/v1]
    CodeFlare -->|manages| AppWrappers[AppWrapper CRs<br/>workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta2]

    RayClusters -.->|creates| RayPods[Ray Head + Workers<br/>+ OAuth Proxy<br/>+ Routes<br/>+ NetworkPolicies]
    AppWrappers -.->|creates| WrappedResources[Wrapped K8s Resources<br/>Jobs, Deployments, etc.]

